channel.title: Fixing Doors and Tele locs. Coords Needed! :)
channel.description:
Ok so me and my mates on my clan server have spent the last week fixing all doors, teleports, and such around our server. yet we're still missing some coordinates to key locations. Such as..
Keldagrim underground temple to morytania = nature spirit quest thing. Zaro's Temple in Digsite
If anyone has these coords, i'd really appreciate it. Not the above ground locations. because as you may or may not be aware, just because the entrance to something is above ground somewhere, doesn't mean the location is right underneath it. Soo.. if you happen to find these coords. thx. :)

item.title: Fixing Doors and Tele locs. Coords Needed! :)
item.dc:creator: @sonjichan sonjichan
item.description:
@sonjichan wrote:

because… those are all underground locations… and I can’t get the position of somewhere i’m not at. also height level commands don’t work for areas like most of those, whereas some places are simply hidden out in the darkness and you’ve gotta find them with ::noclip. I need the coordinates to keldagrim to program the “Door” to keldagrim to transfer my players down there.
